sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Coordinator Agent
    participant T as Telemetry Agent
    participant F as Forecast Agent
    participant R as Root Cause Agent
    participant B as Blast Radius Agent
    participant M as Remediation Agent
    participant P as Report Agent

    C->>T: Collect evidence from Splunk
    T-->>C: Normalized telemetry rows
    C->>F: Forecast risk
    F-->>C: Risk score + level
    C->>R: Rank root causes
    R-->>C: Cause candidates + confidence
    C->>B: Estimate blast radius
    B-->>C: Impact summary
    C->>M: Build remediation plan
    M-->>C: Human-approved recommendation
    C->>P: Generate report
    P-->>C: Markdown report
